sequenceDiagram
  participant Merchant
  participant Wallet
  participant Issuer
  participant Gateway
  participant Service

  Merchant->>Wallet: Handshake request
  Wallet->>Wallet: User reviews request
  Wallet->>Issuer: ACCEPT / REJECT
  Issuer-->>Merchant: Visa token (if accepted)
  Merchant->>Gateway: Request + visa token
  Gateway->>Gateway: Verify token + apply policy
  Gateway->>Service: Forward or route request
